headline: Quanta Services (NYSE:PWR) Sees 15% Stock Price Increase Over Last Week
summary: Quanta Services (NYSE:PWR) saw a notable stock price increase of 15% over the past week. This move aligns with broader market trends, as the Dow Jones and S&P 500 extended their winning streaks amid robust earnings reports and optimism regarding potential tariff adjustments. headline: Quanta to Report Q1 Earnings: What's in the Cards for the Stock?
summary: PWR's Q1 performance is likely to have reflected rising power demand fueled by AI data centers, electrification and the reshoring of manufacturing and acquisitions.
